# Modules vs App Ownership Boundary

- This repository owns business-domain logic, DTO semantics, mappings, and workflow behavior for TPLK.
- `AppModules` owns reusable infrastructure only (call runtime scaffolding, generic observability, technical helper layers).
- Do not move domain value universes or business-specific endpoint semantics into `AppModules`.
- Extract to `AppModules` only when logic is demonstrably domain-agnostic and reusable across multiple apps.
- If a component references patient/condition/procedure domain semantics, keep it in `TPLK-App`.
